QuestData.Title: Reeltime Strategy
QuestData.Description: I never thought I'd see the day, but for the first time since... well, EVER, Master Angler Ju Lien asked for some help with his lines.$B$BApparently the sea is going crazy today and he can't keep up. See if you can give him a hand. He's fishing just south of here.
QuestData.LogDescription: Assist Master Angler Ju Lien in Soggy's Gamble.
QuestData.CompletionText: Go give Ju Lien a hand, would ya?
QuestData.RewardText: What happened out there?! I heard a scream and next thing I know these nasty things come rolling in on the next wave!

Objectives.Objective: Speak with Master Angler Ju Lien
